snippet.title: [ASTRA: Knights of Veda] Special Video | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
The goddess Veda is waiting for you, the master of the 13th book to save the world. 
Become the master of the book, and restore Planis to it's former glory. 
Your adventure, guided by the goddess Veda, begins soon. 

[Official Channels]
Steam: https://bit.ly/3Pla4CB
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/RCpbsE8UQz
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/knightsofveda.en/
